{"tid":1471230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再塞鐵喇各位，幫人免費入閘出閘好過啦！","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:45:10.000Z","uid":294397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4c724e4a9371cd1b91163c14f45b4f5e5f46c97c","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"幫市民檔閘跳閘畀人免費過好過啦<br />\n都係叫不合作運動啫<br />\n有好多人真係手停口停<br />\n咁樣港鐵賺少啲又唔會阻住人<br />\n你知啲人幾鐘意返工架啦...<br />\n雖然係有人體量但真係好大影響架<br />\n幫佢地免費過又唔會畀佢地有籍口話我地阻住哂佢地養家之類 <br />\n而家係要港鐵出黎面對唔係要搞市民啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n利申：TG個塞鐵admin一見到啲人畀啲佢唔啱聽既意見就即block 點樣傾 係咪小朋友黎"},{"pid":"a5ad36c6e386f1725ac41b991fd574a250e16c6f","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:35.000Z","msg":"本身想停上連登一陣都要上黎講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9b4efeb4abf99bbde238b52591024f401a4d7a","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"唔好再塞鐵喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e19b52399b9be2b970d05d443dd1ecb04463b0","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"幫人免費搭車仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f6035a703d65775c89496939f7d2396742a37f","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3e26bfd1432cbb8bbabb5813e74cb643690723","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ad5637c303a1d6cd2da902b8d03eb67db9e645","tid":1471230,"uid":294397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal